  "title": "Security Officer 保安员 (13th month AWS)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>EXCELLENCE NEW ENERGY (SINGAPORE) PTE. LTD. is a subsidiary of Longyan Zhuoyue New Energy Co. LTD, a Shanghai Stock Exchange listed corporation that specializes in the research, development, manufacture, and sales of Biodiesel and derivative products.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are seeking vigilant and responsible Security Officers to maintain safety and security of the factory premises, personnel, and assets through patrols, access control, and enforcement of safety regulations in compliance with Singapore’s security standards.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Conduct regular foot patrols within the factory to monitor and maintain security</li><li>Verify identities and log all vehicles, deliveries, and visitors entering and exiting the factory</li><li>Secure factory entrances during non-operating hours to prevent unauthorized access</li><li>Report and document suspicious activities or security incidents accurately and promptly</li><li>Enforce safety regulations to ensure compliance with Singapore’s security requirements</li><li>Identify potential hazards on site and implement effective solutions to mitigate risks</li><li>Collaborate with team members in a three-person shift rotation to maintain continuous security coverage</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Possess or be willing to obtain the PLRD Certificate (company sponsorship available)</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum of 1 year experience as a Safety Officer in a factory or similar industrial setting</li><li>Ability to communicate effectively in English for clear reporting and coordination</li><li>Own transport to commute to the Tuas work location is advantageous</li></ul><p>Working Hours</p><ul><li>12-hour rotating shifts including weekends and public holidays</li></ul><p>Benefits</p><ul><li>Competitive salary with overtime pay</li><li>Medical and insurance coverage</li><li>Career progression and training opportunities</li><li>Annual Wage Supplement (13th month bonus)</li><li>10 days paid annual leave</li></ul>",
